        "custom_heading": "<p>HOW TO BECOME AN ANIMAL <strong>BRAND AMBASSADOR<\/strong><\/p>",
        "subheading": "We all start somewhere, and then it’s a journey. If your journey has taken you to this web page, then maybe it’s time to take it up a notch. We are looking for serious men and women who are dedicated to the Animal lifestyle and love the brand.",
